Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:42.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早會知道 Vajra真正的恐怖之處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:54.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開拍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是最新型VF-25
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:08.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍攝完成後會用CG加工成VF-0
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡 看見蘭歌沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:13.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌應該在海角那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後還是決定穿女裝？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:21.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:25.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得有幸觀摩傳說中的男旦表演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:29.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉為接受了水下拍攝時的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:30.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替男主角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:33.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是47號鏡頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:38.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真大膽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吻戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:41.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和瑪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 莫非不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:53.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那打算接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼大不了的 接吻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當真？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:05.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佑乘坐的車…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 來人
